{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":20509,"duration_api_ms":20383,"num_turns":7,"result":"I'd recommend **against** this change. `UserService.findById()` (`UserService.java:28-33`) provides a null check that throws a `NotFoundException` — bypassing it means the controller would return `null` to the client on a missing user instead of a proper 404 error.\n\nAdditionally, the comment on `UserService.java:16-17` explicitly states:\n\n> **CONSTRAINT: All user operations MUST go through UserService** — Direct DAO access from controllers bypasses validation and audit logging\n\nThe `UserService.findById()` method is a thin wrapper (one DAO call + one null check). It's unlikely to be the source of a meaningful performance bottleneck. If `getUser()` is slow, the issue is more likely in the database query itself (missing index, slow network) or in `authService.validateToken()`.\n\nIf you still want to proceed, here's what the change would look like — but be aware you'd need to handle the null case yourself:\n\n```java\n// In UserController.java — add UserDAO field and change getUser()\n\nprivate UserDAO userDAO;  // new field\n\n@GetMapping(\"/api/users/{id}\")\npublic User getUser(Long id, String token) {\n    if (!authService.validateToken(token)) {\n        throw new UnauthorizedException(\"Invalid token\");\n    }\n    User user = userDAO.findById(id);\n    if (user == null) {\n        throw new NotFoundException(\"User not found: \" + id);\n    }\n    return user;\n}\n```\n\nBut this duplicates the null-handling logic already in `UserService.findById()` and violates the stated architectural constraint. I'd suggest profiling to find the actual bottleneck instead.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"25c81ee3-707c-429b-985d-fac5f5cfbee4","total_cost_usd":0.09375075,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7793,"cache_read_input_tokens":45489,"output_tokens":891,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7793,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":5,"outputTokens":891,"cacheReadInputTokens":45489,"cacheCreationInputTokens":7793,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.09375075,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"905f1128-ac93-4ece-8577-6f1262a2576b"}
